name: Poster Pack
description:
Get both the ThanksKilling 2 and ThanksKilling 3 posters together at a discounted rate. 

The ThanksKilling 2 posters were made specifically as props for the making of ThanksKilling 3 and were used in the desert sequence where TK2 is destroyed. These are not screen used.

Both posters come rolled. 19" x 27".

*Note: Standard movie poster size is 27" x 41". These posters are slightly smaller than your typical poster but still look great on the wall! For size comparison see picture with the poster next to a standard CD.

***FREE SHIPPING***
